{"tid":1608212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【最新交通消息】九巴、城巴及新巴","createTime":"2019-10-01T08:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T11:00:44.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd6ffc03b9673357513b318d500ef4f4120fded","tid":1608212,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T08:45:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">九巴</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>機場巴士服務</strong><br />\n因應運輸署要求，龍運以下巴士路線將有特別安排。乘客可以於新界乘坐龍運A 線，例如於青衣長安乘坐A31線前往機場客運大樓。<br />\n<br />\n暫停服務：A41/E42/S1/S64<br />\n<br />\n改道行駛：<br />\nE32/E33/E33P/E34A/E34B/E41/E42<br />\n<br />\n往機場/博覽館方向: 改以東涌東堤灣畔為終點站。不停赤鱲角南路至機場地面運輸中心/機場博覽館沿途各站(不經:貨運區、客運大樓及博覽館)<br />\n<br />\n新界方向：維持正常<br />\n<br />\n<strong>過海巴士服務</strong><br />\n乘客可以於灣仔入境事務大樓站乘坐紅隧及東隧路線101/ 104/ 109/ 307/ 601/ 603/ 619/ 673/ 680/ 681/ 690前往九龍及新界各區。<br />\n<br />\n暫停服務：102/103/111/112/113/115/117/170/182/904/905/914/934/936/948/961/978<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九龍市區巴士服務</strong><br />\n暫停服務：2/2F/3C/11C/18/211/214<br />\n<br />\n<strong>荃灣及葵青區巴士服務</strong><br />\n暫停服務：31/32H/33A/34/34M/36/38/38A/39A/40/41M/42C/42M/43/43B/51/234A/234B/234X/238M/243M<br />\n<br />\n<strong>屯門及元朗區巴士服務</strong><br />\n暫停服務：53/61X/62X/67M/67X/258D/259D/261X/263/268C/268M/269C/269D<br />\n<br />\n<strong>沙田，大埔及北區巴士服務</strong><br />\n暫停服務：40X/43X/46X/47A/47X/48X/49X/72/72A/73X/74A/75X/80/80K/80M/80X/81/81K/82B/82K/82X/83K/83X/84M/85/85A/85B/85K/86/86A/86K/87B/88/88K/88X/89/89B/89X/249X/278X/280X/281A/282/283/284/286X/287X/288/289R/299X/888/W3<br />\n<br />\n<strong>西貢區巴士服務</strong><br />\n暫停服務：290/290A/290X<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kmb.hk/tc/news/press/archives/news201910013122.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kmb.hk%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fpress%2Farchives%2Fnews201910013122.html&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9UcscdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=d5fb9720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.kmb.hk/tc/news/press/archives/news201910013122.html</a>"},{"pid":"6cb65af5883543930586eb7057677a464a93d8c2","tid":1608212,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>新巴、城巴</strong></span></span><br />\n（2019 年 10 月 1 日──香港）新巴城巴現時 51 條路線暫停服務，80 多條路線需改道行駛。乘客如要查詢個別路線改道詳情及臨時巴士站安<br />\n排，可使用新巴城巴流動應用程式直接輸入巴士路線查詢。 公司正在因應最新路況作改道應變，改道內容準備好後會盡快更新。<br />\n<br />\n因應香港機場管理局及運輸署的特別交通安排，<span style=\"color: red;\">城巴 S1、S52、S52A 及 S56 號線暫停服務</span>。由市區開出的 E 線班次，改以東涌為終點站。前往機場的乘客，請乘搭城巴機場快線 (「A 線」)。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>暫停服務路線</strong><br />\n1, 2, 5B, 5X, 8H, 11, 12, 12A, 12M, 13, 15B, 15C, X15, X15R, 18P, 18X, 23, 25, 26, 40M, 88R, 103, 104, 111,113, 117, 170, 182, 260, 590, 671, 701, 702, 720, 722, 789, 904, 905, 914, 930, 930X, 948, 967, 970, 970X, 971, 973, S1, S52, S52A, S56, H1, W1 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>改道路線</strong><br />\n2, 2A, 2X, 4, 6, 6X, 7, 8, 8P, 10, 15, 20, 25A, 30X, 37A, 37B, 38, 40, 42, 70, 71, 72, 72A, 75, 76, 77, 81, 90, 90B, 91, 96, 97, 101, 102, 106, 107, 109, 112, 115, 116, 118, 171, 307, 592, 601, 619, 680, 681, 690, 780, 788, 796C, 798, 690, 962B, 962X, 969, A11, A12, A20, B3, B3A, B3M, B3X, A21, A26, A29P, E11, E11A, E21, E21A, E22, E22A, E23, E23A, H2 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nwstbus.com.hk/tc/uploadedPressRelease/14107_201910011545_chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nwstbus.com.hk%2Ftc%2FuploadedPressRelease%2F14107_201910011545_chi.pdf&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9UcscdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=9277d7a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nwstbus.com.hk/tc/uploadedPressRelease/14107_201910011545_chi.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"cf8cc3edeb7cd21df667118027a4037debe666b0","tid":1608212,"uid":69681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T08:48:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1737702a6a4a935644c46a76c5cf28cbcc844884","tid":1608212,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T08:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f44483a3e3cf0f333b20fd6d0fb1cde560cec90","tid":1608212,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e96a5679079d3ad1130a36bc5ea9c91437d8d53","tid":1608212,"uid":118665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T08:53:10.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"069989039b11d324f54d7174847acb4911b2e4dc","tid":1608212,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T08:54:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8e370a850689e8e3907a4e3cd81d3f7bdaed6e5","tid":1608212,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28802ad2ac78efa21d48561bb7240d945d1f36cc","tid":1608212,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26775b4ea965a2480568daea799229a37157d6b6","tid":1608212,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb16b5a7173382bac9001375137a9224302cc45","tid":1608212,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8da670305d704da3919dbf62d826eacae25626","tid":1608212,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:25:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a043921eb1d558273d6d46f1206bededa1e33ae","tid":1608212,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":